Pricing and Support

Explore Ænix Platform pricing. Unlock the full potential of Cozystack platform with enterprise features, flexible billing, SLA-backed commitments, personalized support, and a custom roadmap.

Get started
  1. Incidents related to installation support will not count towards any support incident limit if reported within the 30-day installation support period.
  2. Business hours are defined as Mon–Fri, 9am–6pm CET, excluding holidays.
  3. «Emergency» is defined as an incident involving a production system being down or unresponsive, with no workaround available.
  4. Time we actively dedicate to building features according to your roadmap per month.
